dataIdInfo.idAbs: This line data layer represents roads for Dunn County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Dunn_Roads_2017.gdb.
dataIdInfo.idPurp:
This layer for reference and mapping purposes, and may be used for basic applications such as viewing, querying, and map output production, or to provide a basemap to support graphical overlays and analysis with other spatial data.
[Road centerlines within Dunn County, WI. Revised 03/01/2017. For questions regarding this dataset, please contact the Dunn County Land Information Office at 715-231-6545 or at lis@co.dunn.wi.us.]
